      "x": 95,
      "y": 1180,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 240,
      "text": "RLS (Row Level Security)\n\nTodas las tablas filtran por:\n  organization_id IN\n    (SELECT get_user_org_ids())\n\nTablas con aislamiento:\n  • patients\n  • appointments\n  • doctors\n  • offices\n  • services\n  • global_variables\n  • lookup_categories\n  • lookup_values",
